{"talk":{"id":66828,"name":"Roman Krznaric: How to be a good ancestor","description":"Our descendants own the future, but the decisions and actions we make now will tremendously impact generations to come, says philosopher Roman Krznaric. From a global campaign to grant legal personhood to nature to a groundbreaking lawsuit by a coalition of young activists, Krznaric shares examples of ways we can become good ancestors -- or, as he calls them, \"Time Rebels\" -- and join a movement redefining lifespans, pursuing intergenerational justice and practicing deep love for the planet.","slug":"roman_krznaric_how_to_be_a_good_ancestor","recorded_at":"2020-10-10 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-10-23 14:45:53","updated_at":"2020-12-30 11:47:26","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":620,"name":"Countdown"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/391a1c045143877b247fc040f94ac0247b586eb1_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/391a1c045143877b247fc040f94ac0247b586eb1_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/391a1c045143877b247fc040f94ac0247b586eb1_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/391a1c045143877b247fc040f94ac0247b586eb1_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/9cebf9ff8b2f0172a770367b95f175d881ab93fa_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/RomanKrznaric_2020T-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":3580159,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/RomanKrznaric_2020T-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":9859425,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/RomanKrznaric_2020T-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":17449412,"mime_type":"video\